text: The Sula is a river in Nenets Autonomous Okrug and Komi Republic, Russia. It is a left tributary of the Pechora, flowing into its left branch Borshchyovy Shar near Velikovisochnoye, Nenets Autonomous Okrug. It is long, and has a drainage basin of . ==References== Category:Rivers of the Komi Republic Category:Rivers of Nenets Autonomous Okrug
